text: Tricondyloides caledonicus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1947.BioLib.cz - Tricondyloides caledonicus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1947
